title: (Fri Early Bird) Bobby Receiving Honorary Doctorate Tomorrow! Country Artists Who Have Received the Same Honor + Mailbag: Is 40 Too Old To Make New Friends? + Easy Trivia!
itunes:title: (Fri Early Bird) Bobby Receiving Honorary Doctorate Tomorrow! Country Artists Who Have Received the Same Honor + Mailbag: Is 40 Too Old To Make New Friends? + Easy Trivia!
description:
Bobby is just a day away from receiving his honorary doctorate from the University of Arkansas. Amy shares a list of country artists who have received the same honor. In the mailbag, a wife says her husband is refusing to join a golf club because he thinks 40 is too old to make new friends. And we play a round of Easy Trivia.
